events.description: Pre-registration rewards are now available for all players who install and log in before Monday, September 25, 2023, at 11:59 p.m. (UTC). Rewards must be claimed from the in-game shop before Thursday, November 30, 2023, at 11:59 p.m. (local time). Rewards include Potion x10, Paintball x3, Wander Droplet x3, Special Pre-order Makeup x4, Item Box Expansion x500, and Special Carving Knife x3.
